title: Sexy Berkeley (Sexy #1)by Dani Lovell
description:
A long-distance relationship with a hot American
businessman is the last thing on Beatrice Hart's
mind when the day from hell ends with her drink-
booking a last minute escape to glamorous
Southern California.With Bea's firm belief that long
distance never works, will she ever consider that
that an exhilarating introduction at 35,000 feet could
lead to anything more than a steamy holiday romance?
Daniel Berkeley is the irresistible, delectable, smoking
hot bachelor, determined to make it happen.
